(57611, 166254, 5421, 1, 'Bear Feet', '', '2011-12-01 00:00:00', 2011, 25, 0, 5, 'It''s cold out and I see three kids jumping in the rain \r\n冷天，三个孩子跳入雨中\r\nOne falls down not knowing who to blame \r\n一个跌倒不知怪谁\r\nThe simple things that hurt us everyday \r\n最简单的事伤我们最深\r\nAs I go out he says that he''s ok but have you got the time \r\n他还好，但是问我是否有时间\r\nI said it''s late kid I think it’s time you run on home \r\n很晚了孩子，你该回家了\r\n\r\nHis friends were gone I walked him so he didn''t walk alone \r\n他的朋友已经离去，我送他回家\r\nHis mother greeted him at the front door \r\n他的妈妈在门口等他\r\nShe thanked me twice and asked me to stay for supper \r\n她谢了我问我能否留下吃饭\r\nI could see that she was mourning for his dad \r\n我看得出她在悼念孩子的父亲\r\nYou could see it in her eyes \r\n从她的双眼 映出悲伤\r\nShe would blink to disguise that she cries \r\n眨眼，伪装坚强\r\nSo I stayed for an hour or two \r\n我呆了一会\r\nKept them company for a while and made the little boy smile \r\n陪他们一会，逗笑了小男孩\r\n\r\nAs I left my voice was shaking and nothing was as it seemed \r\n我的声音在颤抖，一切都那么不真实\r\nI hear my phone ringing, it wakes me from my dream \r\n我听见铃声，从梦中醒来\r\nIt was just a dream about humanity \r\n仅仅是一个关于人性的梦\r\nHelp a stranger cross the street \r\n帮助陌生人过马路\r\nGive him shoes to bear his feet \r\n给他一双鞋来走路\r\nOn your final day do you think you''ll say \r\n在你的最后一天你觉得你会说\r\nThat you helped someone in need or was your life controlled by greed?\r\n你帮助过什么人或者你的人生被贪婪吞噬？\r\n', '', 240, '', '', '', '', 'Independent', '', 0, 0, 0, '2012-12-19 10:16:11', '2015-03-12 13:57:44', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(57612, 166254, 5421, 2, 'Haunting Blues', '', '2011-12-01 00:00:00', 2011, 25, 0, 5, 'I''m looking for a way to decay my crooked past \r\n追寻赎罪的路\r\nMaybe someone’s out to get me, but if I hide I''ll never last \r\n也许需要谁的帮助，在躲藏里我永远坚持不到最后\r\nSaid I''m a weak man but I''m holding on \r\n我太脆弱，但是我能坚持\r\nCause’ I''m too tired to be afraid no more \r\n一直害怕的日子我受够了\r\nSo I''m going to sit right here and just sing along \r\n我要坐在这一个人歌唱\r\n\r\nTake me to beloved Cherry Hill \r\n带我去我爱的樱桃山吧\r\nTake the paper bag off from my face and let the oil spill (start a fire) \r\n撕掉我伪装的面具，点起火吧\r\nLaugh at me and choke against my will \r\n嘲笑我，让我窒息吧\r\nI''m going down into the absolute \r\n我一定走得更远\r\n\r\nPicking out the faults in you will show the fault in me \r\n你的错也是我的错\r\nI''ve been wrong about a billion times again and again \r\n我一直在错\r\nI''m a coward conquer cutting everyone \r\n我是一个懦弱的小丑\r\nAnd the blues will stay, it won''t go away \r\n蓝色将永远不会离去\r\nUntil someone slays me with a righteous tongue \r\n直到有人用正义置我于死地\r\n\r\nIf you close your eyes and think about me still \r\n如果你闭上眼睛只想起我\r\nYou''ll know just where to find me on beloved Cherry Hill \r\n你会直到在我爱的樱桃山能找到我\r\nIf you’re bound to lose your temper I guess that’s how you feel \r\n我知道你会发怒\r\nBecause I''m not inclined to waste my time on something that ain''t real \r\n因为我没有浪费时间在幻觉上\r\nAnd there''s ten men out to get me and I guarantee they will \r\n我保证 将有十个人将会帮助我 \r\nThey can burn my soul to kingdom come and I would understand \r\n他们会燃烧我的灵魂 我会理解\r\nBut if you''ve got a love for anything come and join us if you will \r\n如果你想来加入我们吧\r\nWe''re going down so don''t push me round\r\n我们将往下走去，别拉住我\r\n', '', 173, '', '', '', '', 'Independent', '', 0, 0, 0, '2012-12-19 10:26:42', '2015-03-12 13:57:44', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(57613, 166254, 5421, 3, 'River Bend', '', '2011-12-01 00:00:00', 2011, 25, 0, 5, 'Oh you’re the blackest soul \r\n哦你有最坏的灵魂\r\nFor something that I’m not \r\n我却不是\r\nYou’re a river bend down the end \r\n你是小河最后的曲折\r\nThat makes us so far gone \r\n让我们走了这么远\r\n\r\nOh yeah we smile a lot \r\n我们笑很多\r\nWe all do as we like \r\n我们只做自己喜爱的事\r\nMy mother said don’t reveal\r\n我妈妈说悄悄地 \r\nThe secrets sealed in the bag you filled \r\n秘密将在你填满的包里被掩埋\r\n\r\nI got a funny feeling \r\n我觉得搞笑\r\nI’ve got a nerve, I’ve got a knack \r\n我觉得紧张，我有一个诀窍\r\nI sliced and cut and split her gut \r\n我撕裂她的身体\r\nAnd as she turned she shot me in the back \r\n她转身向我开枪\r\nWe just smile and dig our names in hell \r\n我们微笑，将自己的名字刻入地狱\r\nMy father used to be just like me and mess around \r\n我爸爸以前就像我一样随便\r\nBut I could never tell \r\n但是我永远不知道\r\n\r\nWon’t you bring down the weather \r\n你能带走这坏天气\r\nSo I can see a bit more clear\r\n所以我能看的更清楚 \r\nI draped my arms in leather\r\n我躲在皮具后 \r\nFor about a year\r\n大概一年过去 \r\n\r\nOh yeah we smile a lot \r\n哦，我们微笑\r\nAnd we all do as we like\r\n我们做自己想做的 \r\nMy mother said don’t reveal \r\n我妈妈说悄悄地 \r\n\r\nThe secrets sealed in the bag you filled\r\n秘密将在你填满的包里被掩埋\r\n', '', 245, '', '', '', '', 'Independent', '', 0, 0, 0, '2012-12-19 10:30:29', '2015-03-12 13:57:44', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(57614, 166254, 5421, 4, 'Silver Liquid', '', '2011-12-01 00:00:00', 2011, 0, 2, 5, 'Listen to your maker \r\n听你的创造者\r\nThe shadows keep you safer\r\n阴影让你安全 \r\nGentle is the giant\r\n温和是一个巨人 \r\nThat claims he put you here \r\n他带你来这\r\nWell my night sky’s oblivion while \r\n我的夜晚天空被遗忘\r\nI lie oblivious inside \r\n我躺在遗忘的中央\r\nI''ve lost my mind but I’m fine\r\n忘记了所有，没事\r\nI''ll just enjoy time while it’s gone \r\n我将享受所有将要逝去的时光\r\nThe room fills up with light as a taxi waits outside \r\n光充满了屋子，车等在外边\r\nAll the walls seem bright while my future’s black and white \r\n我的未来灰暗没有颜色但是周围的墙看上去无比明亮\r\n\r\nSometimes I wonder if the palings on my fence just keep me in \r\n有时我想周围的栅栏围住了我\r\nCaged up wonder curiously looks out but then stays in \r\n被围住的我充满好奇的想去外面\r\nNo one would believe it \r\n没人相信\r\n\r\nQuiet’s the pacifist mind \r\n安静是最和平的心\r\nNo better way to spend my time \r\n没法更好的打发时间\r\nMy soul’s been purified now\r\n我的灵魂现在已经纯净 \r\nNo longer dead since she arrived\r\n她的到来给了我再生 \r\nOur blood runs silver liquid\r\n我们的血液像流动的银色\r\n \r\nThrough the cracks of our old existence \r\n从我们过去腐烂的存在里\r\nOn this road together \r\n一起走在这条路上\r\nWill you forgive a sinner? \r\n你会原谅一个罪人么\r\n\r\nThe room fills up with light as a taxi waits outside \r\n光充满了屋子，车等在外边\r\n\r\nAll the walls seem bright while my future’s black and white\r\n我的未来 灰暗没有颜色  周围的墙却无比明亮\r\n', '', 170, '', '', '', '', 'Independent', '', 0, 0, 0, '2012-12-19 10:41:03', '2015-03-12 13:57:45', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(57615, 166254, 5422, 1, 'Cup of Nestor', '', '2012-06-01 00:00:00', 2012, 0, 2, 5, 'I dreamt last night \r\n昨夜的梦\r\nIt was the end of the world\r\n仿佛是世界的尽头\r\nAnd I forgot about you while I was trying to save my soul\r\n在努力拯救自己的灵魂时我忘了你\r\nI stood there alone\r\n孤零零的站在那\r\nAs the house fell down around me\r\n仿佛周围的建筑都围着我倒下\r\n\r\nIs this revelry or am I living a lie?\r\n这是什么样的狂欢还是我从未从谎言中醒来？\r\nCause I don’t want to wait unit I wake up, for I might die\r\n我不想醒来，因为可能我会死去\r\nDown the chimney reaches a hand\r\n一双手从烟囱伸出\r\nPulls me up above land\r\n拉我离开地面\r\n\r\nThere’s a chalice full\r\n这有杯圣酒\r\nAnd it can be my muse\r\n它是我的MUSE\r\nAnd if we all drink from it will we speak the truth\r\n喝下它我们只吐真言\r\n\r\nEveryone join hands\r\n所有人拉起手\r\nEveryone join hands\r\n所有人拉起手\r\nEveryone join hands\r\n所有人拉起手\r\nEveryone join hands\r\n所有人拉起手\r\n\r\nI pray that I\r\n我祈祷\r\nI pray that I will find my way\r\n我祈祷我能找到光明\r\nAnd I pray that I\r\n我祈祷\r\nI pray that I will find my way\r\n我祈祷我能找到光明\r\nI pray that I, pray that I will find my way\r\n我祈祷我能找到光明\r\nI pray that I, pray that I will find my way\r\n我祈祷我能找到光明\r\nI pray that I, pray that I will find my way home\r\n我祈祷我能找到回家的路\r\n', '', 287, '', '', '', '', 'Independent', '', 0, 0, 0, '2012-12-19 10:55:29', '2015-03-12 13:57:45', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(57616, 166254, 5422, 2, 'Paint The Sky', '', '2012-06-01 00:00:00', 2000, 0, 2, 5, 'Can you believe I sold my soul\r\n 相信么我出卖了自己的灵魂\r\nI caught the devil in my house once more\r\n又一次抓住了自己的恶魔\r\nAnd my girl, she turned to dust\r\n我心爱的女孩  化为灰烬\r\nThen an image unfolds of the loneliest soul\r\n只剩下我一个人孤独的灵魂\r\nAnd I’m left with no one I can trust\r\n这个世界我再也没人能够相信\r\n\r\nOh lie, lie, lie\r\n哦，谎言，谎言，谎言\r\nWe all never cry\r\n我们永远不会哭泣\r\nAnd my body’s only half as old but the whole world knows\r\n我还年轻全世界都知道\r\nYeah the whole world knows\r\n是的，全世界都知道\r\nOh lie, lie, lie\r\n哦，谎言谎言，谎言\r\nForget about my reputation\r\n忘了人们怎么说我吧\r\n\r\nWhat I call my night is when I see my sun\r\n太阳升起时就是我的黑夜的到来\r\nThe river is going black so you better turn and run\r\n河水变黑，你最好快点走吧\r\nAnd it might be hell that’s keeping you so steady\r\n也许是地狱让你一直留在这\r\nAnd we’ve been coming here a long, long time\r\n从我们来着算起已经是很久很久了\r\nBut you never leave my high without my halo on\r\n我的光环从未离去，你也从未离开\r\n\r\nOh lie, lie, lie\r\n哦，谎言谎言，谎言\r\nWe all never cry\r\n我们不会哭泣\r\nAnd my body’s only half as old but the whole world knows\r\n我还年轻全世界都知道\r\nYeah the whole world knows\r\n是的，全世界都知道\r\nOh lie, lie, lie\r\n哦，谎言谎言，谎言\r\n\r\nAll the things I’ve found\r\n那些我发现的事\r\nThe question on my mind\r\n那些我曾有的疑问\r\nAm I living a lie?\r\n也许我生活在谎言里\r\nHey devil where did you come from?\r\n恶魔啊，你到底从哪里来？\r\nHey devil where did you go?\r\n恶魔啊，你要去哪呢？\r\nDevil where did you come from?\r\n恶魔啊，你从哪里来？\r\n\r\n\r\nOh lie, lie, lie\r\n哦，谎言谎言，谎言\r\nWe all never cry\r\n我们不会哭泣\r\nAnd my body’s only half as old but the whole world knows\r\n我还年轻全世界都知道\r\nYeah the whole world knows\r\n是的，全世界都知道\r\nOh lie, lie, lie\r\n哦，谎言谎言，谎言\r\n\r\n\r\nWe all never cry\r\n我们永不哭泣\r\nWe all never cry\r\n我们永不哭泣\r\nWe all never cry\r\n我们永不哭泣\r\nWe all never cry\r\n我们永不哭泣\r\n', '', 217, '', '', '', '', 'Independent', '', 0, 0, 0, '2012-12-19 11:02:34', '2015-03-12 13:57:45', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(57617, 166254, 5422, 3, 'Say You Love Me Too', '', '2012-06-01 00:00:00', 2000, 0, 2, 5, 'I’ve been sleeping with a ghost\r\n我一直和鬼在一起睡\r\nI can feel it while I dream\r\n梦中我能感觉到它\r\nThen I wake and it leaves\r\n我醒来，它离去\r\nGives me no time to speak of errors in what we had\r\n没有机会让我说出我们之间的不对\r\n\r\nI haven’t spoken to my friends\r\n我没和别人说\r\nI don’t like to bother them\r\n谁都不想麻烦\r\nFickle mindset takes it\r\n变幻无常的心默默承受\r\nNow I want to touch her skin\r\n这一刻我想能够触摸到她\r\nI want to breathe again\r\n我想再一次呼吸\r\n\r\nOh she’s all that I need\r\n哦，她是我的全部\r\nSometimes I cry\r\n我忍不住的哭泣\r\n\r\nAnd I’ve been looking at my face\r\n我默默看着自己的脸，\r\nA lot of changing in days\r\n变化很多\r\nNothing occupies my eyes\r\n我的眼睛里只剩下空洞\r\nNo love, no soul, just glass\r\n没有爱，没有灵魂，只有玻璃球\r\nOver empty pools\r\n什么都没有的空白\r\n\r\nOh she’s all that I need\r\n哦，我只需要她\r\nSometimes I cry\r\n我忍不住的哭泣\r\n\r\n\r\nHow long before\r\n多久以前\r\nWondering I walk into you\r\n我遇见你\r\nI’ve been here before\r\n我来过这\r\nThe never-ending road winding through\r\n这条永远没有尽头的路\r\nI cry\r\n哭泣\r\n\r\nJust say you love me too\r\n说你也爱我\r\nJust say you love me too\r\n说你也爱我\r\nJust say you love me too\r\n说你也爱我\r\n\r\nHow long before\r\n多久以前\r\nWondering I walk into you\r\n我遇见你\r\nI’ve been here before\r\n我来过这\r\nThe never-ending road winding through\r\n这条永远没有尽头的路\r\n\r\nHow pure is the soul\r\n多么纯净的灵魂\r\nThat leaves my night the brightest\r\n留光明给我的夜晚\r\nThe brightest of blue\r\n那最鲜艳的蓝色\r\nIn the dark so far away\r\n在黑夜中是那么遥远\r\nThe passions present clear\r\n激动的心摇摇欲坠\r\nCome tomorrow\r\n明天再来\r\nA love reappears\r\n为了爱再出现一次\r\nJust say you love me too\r\n说吧，只要你说你也爱我\r\n', '', 227, '', '', '', '', 'Independent', '', 0, 0, 0, '2012-12-19 11:08:03', '2015-03-12 13:57:45', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
